data.text:
Xinetd Service

<Xinetd Service> objects represent Unix xinetd (extended Internet daemon) services.

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

Creation

xinetd service : Xinetd Service

Returns all xinetd services.

Plural: xinetd services

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

xinetd service <string> : Xinetd Service

Retrurns the xinetd service corresponding to the name provided.

Plural: xinetd services

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

Properties

disabled of <Xinetd Service> : boolean

Returns True if the service is disabled.

Plural: disableds

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

flag of <Xinetd Service> : string

Returns the flags for the service.

Plural: flags

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu

id of <Xinetd Service> : string

Returns the id of the service.

Plural: ids

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

name of <Xinetd Service> : string

Returns the name of the service.

Plural: names

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

no access of <Xinetd Service> : string

Returns the 'no_access' blacklist of hosts that are not allowed to use this service.

Plural: no accesses

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

only from of <Xinetd Service> : string

Returns the 'only_from' whitelist of hosts that are allowed to use this service.

Plural: only froms

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

port of <Xinetd Service> : integer

Returns the port number that this service uses.

Plural: ports

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

protocol of <Xinetd Service> : string

Returns the protocol that this service uses.

Plural: protocols

Version Platforms 9.2.7.53 Debian, Red Hat, SUSE, Ubuntu 9.5.13.130 Raspbian

server arg of <Xinetd Service> : string

server of <Xinetd Service> : string

socket type of <Xinetd Service> : string

type of <Xinetd Service> : string

user of <Xinetd Service> : string

wait of <Xinetd Service> : boolean
